msgid "Comic Book Creation Tool"
msgstr "Orodje za ustvarjanje stripov"

#. (itstool) path: description/p
#: org.kde.perusecreator.appdata.xml:10
msgid ""
"Creating rich digital comic books has long been something of a chore, or "
"required the use of proprietary formats, but the Advanced Comic Book Format "
"aims to fix this by introducing concepts like frame based navigation to go "
"with the more traditional page based methods, reference information such as "
"character information, location notes, and so on, all contained within the "
"book, as well as embedded typesetting information and rich text overlays so "
"translation can be done without requiring multiple images of the same page. "
"Peruse Creator allows you to create these highly interactive and advanced "
"books in a way which is both easy to use, and powerful."
msgstr ""
"Ustvarjanje bogatih digitalnih stripov je že dolgo kar naporno ali pa "
"zahteva uporabo lastniških zapisov, vendar je cilj naprednega zapisa stripov "
"to popraviti z uvedbo konceptov, kot so krmarjenje, ki temelji na sličicah, "
"ki gre skupaj z bolj tradicionalnimi metodami, ki temeljijo na straneh, "
"referenčne informacije, kot so podatki o liku, opombe o lokaciji itn., vse "
"skupaj pa v obliki knjige, skupaj z vdelanimi podatki o stavljenju in "
"prekrivno obogatenim besedilom, tako da je mogoče opraviti prevod, ne da bi "
"to zahtevalo več slik iste strani. Peruse Creator omogoča, da ustvarite te "
"zelo interaktivne in napredne knjige na način, ki je enostaven za uporabo in "
"ponuja veliko možnosti."

